<br>
I have all the stuff needed to trigger the Kurron Ni fight, however, I'm still using some of those items, so for now, that particular epic encounter can wait.<br>
<br>
I still need two planar drops (Blade of Abrogation from Air, and the Soul Leach from Fear) but those I will eventually get if we keep doing open raids and I keep attending them.<br>
<br>
An epic raid on the Hole would be nice.  I know a few epic items are needed there, including the Dusty Tome I still need (drops off ratman guards) and the Cell Key (drops off mimics) needed to trigger Kyrenna who drops the Blood of Kyrenna and the Heart of Kyrenna.  I still need all of those things.  2-3 strong groups will probably be needed to do all of that.<br>
<br>
Also I need the Drake Spine which drops off Rharzar in the Rathe Mountains.  Two strong groups would probably suffice against him. <p><B><FONT FACE="Comic Sans MS">--Tukka</FONT></B><BR>
